Pending/Incomplete: Tasks that are yet to be completed.
Completed: Tasks that have been finished.
In Progress: Tasks that are currently being worked on.
On Hold: Tasks that are temporarily suspended or delayed.
Canceled/Abandoned: Tasks that have been canceled or abandoned.
Deferred: Tasks that have been postponed to a later time.
Scheduled: Tasks that are scheduled to be completed at a specific date or time.
Waiting: Tasks that are waiting for some external event or input before they can be worked on.



priority; // e.g., 'High', 'Medium', 'Low'